node.title: F1's crazy season comes to an end with one race for the championship
node.alt: Two racing drivers in composite head shots
node.description: Will Lewis Hamilton stand alone as the most successful Formula 1 driver in history or can Max Verstappen dethrone the Mercedes king? Follow live.
node.content: ["Formula 1's chaotic, dramatic and tightest season comes down to the final race.", "Will Lewis Hamilton stand alone as the most successful Formula 1 driver in history or can Max Verstappen dethrone the Mercedes king?", "Follow the title-decider as it happens on our live blog.\u00a0"]
